subject_information.comments: I wish that it could have lasted longer.  It ended much too soon so I was not able to enjoy it as much as I had hoped.  Thank you for the opportunity!
subject_information.strategy: I wasn't able to use much strategy as the other person disconnected right away.  I was hoping to chat with the person and try to figure out a good way to relay the info.  It didn't last very long unfortunately.
